items.badge_description: So, you're new around here? Congrats on your first brew! This one's for you.

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 225 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 46!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 305 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 62!

items.checkin_comment: Different. Smells like a sour - but tastes ok.
